###  Evaluation Trial Instances

#### Trial 1: Training CAD Tool (Progressive)
data:Trial_TrainingCADTool rdf:type guide:EvaluationTrial ;
                           sch:name "Training CAD Tool" ;
                           data:eventIndex 4 ; # From table row Sem=4, Activity Type 2 column has training in week 3/4? Table shows Sem 1-17. Trial is listed as Sem 4 in evaluation section but schedule says Week 3 or 4. I will use the Evaluation Section reference for trial ID if available.
                           guide:trialType "Prueba Telemática" ;
                           guide:trialMode "No Presencial" ;
                           om:activityDurationUnit <http://www.ontology-of-units-of-measure.org/resource/om-2/hour> .


#### Trial 1 Details (from Section 7 Table)
data:Trial_TrainingCADTool rdf:type guide:EvaluationTrial, sch:EventSchedule ;
                           data:eventIndex 4 ; # Based on table row Sem=4 in Evaluation section? Actually evaluation trials are listed by Semester. I will link to ScheduleEvent if possible or just define as Trial instance linked via hasEvaluationTrial property (which is not defined for CourseGuide but for EvaluationSystem). Ontology says `guide:hasEvaluationTrial` domain `guide:EvaluationSystem`.
                           guide:evaluationDuration "03:00" ;
                           guide:gradePercentage 10.0 ;
                           guide:minimumScore "0 / 10"@en .


